  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is described in the validation narrative and applied to selected operating points; however, not all validation results carry formal UQ artifact linkage. Full 13-factor assessment performed. Decision: Accepted based on aggregate credibility evidence.",
