      "description": "CFD-predicted NIH compared against in-vitro measurement at 6 L/min, 2800 RPM. Predicted NIH = 0.0053 g/100L; measured NIH = 0.0049 ± 0.0005 g/100L. Relative error 8.2%. Uncertainty in hemolysis prediction at this condition is discussed qualitatively in the validation report; variability in red blood cell damage model coefficients is acknowledged as a contributor to prediction spread. No formal UQ artifact was linked to this result at the time of assessment.",
      "hasUncertaintyQuantification": "https://uofa.net/synth/uq/mc-propagation-6lpm-2800rpm"
